            <h3>üí° Remember:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Pret√©rito pluscuamperfecto formation for <strong>ellos/ellas</strong>: <strong>hab√≠an</strong> + past participle</li>
                <li>For reflexive verbs, place <strong>se</strong> before <strong>hab√≠an</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Antes de</strong> is used to express "before" in time sequences</li>
                <li>Common past participles: <strong>convertido</strong> (convertir), <strong>jugado</strong> (jugar), <strong>visto</strong> (ver), <strong>entrenado</strong> (entrenar)</li>
                <li>The pluscuamperfecto is used to express actions that had occurred before another past action</li>
            </ul>
